Params[3]: There are no others in sight except Ayla in the long and narrow space station passageway.
The lights flicker on and off. Dull, low battle noises could be heard occasionally, probably coming from other troops fighting the enemy.
Ayla inhales a deep breath and starts to focus, trying to sense any possible signal from Selena.
Ayla tries all sorts of communication methods but receives no replies.
Maybe Selena can't receive any signals... Yes, that must be it.
It's okay... I will find you, and I will bring you back...
Keep it up, Selena. Keep singing...
Ayla picks up her scythe and starts running...
